I wasn't planning to release a 480p
This was a test encoded for a larger project,
that came out good enough to share.


English Subs Hardcoded for Non-English Dialogue


Special thanks to "monodioo" for providing translations, where needed.
Standard Blu-Ray subtitles did not translate all dialogue.
These were translated from a Vietnamese subtitle, 
which covered all dialogue in the movie.
